{"tid":313581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學請助理教師兼學校維修員 upgrade咗個名 實際係...","createTime":"2017-07-08T12:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T19:24:37.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d98f3b1fbfd946a38271c5eb45ab3156638584","tid":313581,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"教席不足，以致即使受過師訓的教師，只能擔任教學助理，期望有日可以晉升成常額教師。然而，近日有中學聘請「助理教師兼學校維修員」，要求應徵者熟悉文書處理又要有電工牌照，究竟工種屬教師抑或技工？<br />\n刊登招聘廣告的中華基督教會扶輪中學校長歐陽家強解釋，「個名upgrade 咗叫助理教師，其實係科技助理嚟嘅。」作為辦學團體校董之一的前立法會議員黃成智則指，「個名唔重要。」<br />\n教協會長馮偉華指，實質上亦無「助理教師」職級，只有「教學助理」，而工種屬技術員，直斥廣告誤導。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/687945/xlarge/39541e554b430d387278ab510d7ec7ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F687945%2Fxlarge%2F39541e554b430d387278ab510d7ec7ab.jpg&h=47cc48cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e5a945fd6fd6780920c5311d329768f5a5ede94","tid":313581,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4285bbf8085f73127a178f4ce4b9a7c66c46ba7","tid":313581,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又IT又電工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIronman"},{"pid":"a9f69a07feb1b5c7b9dfdb086f403746f9a98e8b","tid":313581,"uid":52605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"兩隻字 校工"},{"pid":"c7f2a8a2c930f3a8a9dbc297f6714f253c22ade9","tid":313581,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"Title唔重要 但你第日出返黎HR狗睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069b73a800851d8c5588c19bae24260fa3ab5174","tid":313581,"uid":53648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db09ced646c063b3d38c15cd1570c